Teleglobe Canada Inc, owned by MemotecData Inc (MDI.M), said it received an order from CreditLyonnais Canada for a direct satellite link between Canada andFrance that will be the first private satellite network betweenthe two countries.    Value of the contract was undisclosed.    Teleglobe said the connection will provide the bank with apermanent link to the digital phone switch at its parentcompany's Paris headquarters and connect it with CreditLyonnais' network in France and the rest of the world. Reuter&#3;